      <div className="fn">Traditional 401(k)/IRA: pre-tax — reduces AGI immediately, taxed on withdrawal. Roth 401(k)/IRA: after-tax — no current deduction, but all growth and qualified withdrawals are tax-free. HSA: triple advantage — deductible contributions, tax-free growth, tax-free withdrawals for medical. 401(k) limit applies to combined Traditional + Roth contributions.</div>
